Module gamecritic

Package gui_interfaces

package gui_interfaces
Package used to organize interfaces related to gui components of application. Interfaces in this package define gui behavior, styling, and logic, that can be implemented in various parts to maintain consistency and modularity.
  • Interfaces
    Class
    Description
    FieldInterface
    Interface that extends StyleInterface by inheriting its constants, and defines methods to set the styles of field elements depending on the state of data validation.
    StyleInterface
    Interface that defines set of constant string values and methods.
    ToolBarInterface
    Interface defining methods for standard toolbar buttons within the application's gui.
